；清乾隆年間人民恐懼妖術，相傳術士呼喊人的名字，夜晚來割頭髮辮子，村民在恐慌之下趕走外客，不准剃頭講護家。此「疫病」波及十三省，乾隆下令調查，發現只是流言。上世紀五十年代，華南及南洋爆發縮陽事件，特別是海南和廣東南部差不多每隔十年爆發一次，患者恐懼陽物變小甚至消失，這是以焦慮和驚恐為特徵的心因性障礙。例如海南和雷州半島在1985年3、4月間，就爆發過一次流行性的「縮陽症」。中國今日全國驅逐湖北人，當街毆打武漢人，也是集體瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">你睇完會唔會覺得精神病會傳染？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"90ba193d8d0b21ea8702b4e3e5b2924360f8e0ed","tid":1970711,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be2aafc573e832a4cb5d1270702b43f4477d84d6","tid":1970711,"uid":37528,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"K Kwong都忍唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f8695c22cc6fa7235e4ad2776186d27d2ff88c","tid":1970711,"uid":291065,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"班云粉好似中左邪咁點會聽丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9222484856ad70b8182ba1185b3792d5ad880ce","tid":1970711,"uid":304856,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"be2aafc573e832a4cb5d1270702b43f4477d84d6","tid":1970711,"uid":37528,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"K Kwong都忍唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"緊係忍唔撚到啦，你試下日日俾人話你五毛，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo